PREAMBLE

This Software License Agreement ("Agreement") governs the use, reproduction,
modification, distribution, sublicensing, and commercialization of the software,
source code, object code, algorithms, datasets, model weights, configuration
files, documentation, interfaces, and all associated assets (collectively, the
"Software") developed, maintained, or distributed by NuRichter Workspace.

NuRichter Workspace develops software and systems spanning artificial intelligence
and machine learning, Internet of Things (IoT), electrical engineering, creative
design, and technical education. The Software covered by this Agreement reflects
substantial investment in research, engineering labor, and intellectual capital
by NuRichter and its contributors.

This Agreement is designed to balance the open-source ethos of permissive
distribution with the legitimate commercial, reputational, and legal interests
of NuRichter Workspace and the broader contributor community. By obtaining a
copy of the Software, you ("Licensee", "User", "Recipient") agree unconditionally
to all terms set forth herein.

IF YOU DO NOT AGREE TO THESE TERMS IN FULL, YOU MUST IMMEDIATELY CEASE ALL
USE OF THE SOFTWARE AND DESTROY ALL COPIES IN YOUR POSSESSION OR CONTROL.

